children.value: Meet Leonard the lion! Have you ever met a lion who didn't eat meat? Meet Leonard, he's a vegetarian! He loves lentils, lasagna, and learning how to code. Leonard loves naps like his older brother Richard and is helping create their website – the lion brothers! He is the younger brother of Richie-kun.
Richard spends his days napping and his nights working as a security guard. His favorite color is orange and even though helooks tough, this lion is a big softy. He is the big brother of Leo-kun.
